name: @BoredApe9460 on Tour // Unsplash.com
description: Photo by Eric Ward @ericjamesward // Berlin, Germany // 1 of 1 Remix created by @FutureNow_Art, co-owners of #BAYC 9460 // We created a video for a German startup company called Hackerbay - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VoC9JNk90zQ - telling the story of Banksy’s Balloon Girl not following the corporate path and finding her true passion in life. This is Hacker Culture, a brand mission to redefine the term ‘hacker’.
